    • overlaps

      public boolean overlaps(javafx.collections.ObservableList<Appointments> appointments)
      Checks to see if an appointment overlaps with any in the observable list. A series of logical checks is used to compare start and end times. If there is an overlap, true is returned, otherwise false is.
      Parameters:
      appointments - An ObservableList of appointments
      Returns:
      true of there is an overlap and false if not
